# Changelog

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## [Unreleased] - 2025-02-22

### Added
- Made Simba a pipâ€‘installable package, simplifying installation and integration.
- Added support for multiple embeddings and LLM providers through improved factory design.

### Changed
- Refactored the codebase for better integration and maintainability.
- Simplified the configuration file for easier setup and customization.

### Fixed
- Improved factories to correctly support different embeddings and LLMs.
- Adjusted Celery integration by removing forced CPU-only support to allow more flexible runtime behavior.

## [1.0.0] - 2025-02-21
### Added
- Initial release of Simba with core features: ingestion, parsing, retrieval, and default chatbot integration.